data.description: Property with not one but two homes on 4.83 acres! Featuring 3 bedrooms and 1 bath large kitchen and carport. The home also has a cellar!  Beautiful pine walls and lots of room to roam outside. 1982 Mobile Home is 4 bedrooms and 2 baths but has been completely gutted, ready for you to make your own! Let this property work for you.
